I&#39;ve been using it for nine months,  and then it got a glitch. 
I sought the online support, &#34;It won&#39;t charge properly, could you fix that? I understand its maintenance was expired.&#34;
One minute later, I got a reply, &#34;Send it back to us, we&#39;ll replace a new one for you.&#34;
Thumbs up to Yanxuan service.
